<div class="mntl-sc-block-universal-callout__body"><ul><li>Cocoa, eggs, and simple pantry staples mix into a light, fluffy, fun play on traditional waffles.</li><li>Whip these waffles up anytime to make breakfast feel special, and watch them become a family favorite.</li><li>&#34;My children really enjoyed these….&#34; —Allrecipes member ScottFamily.</li></ul></div>
</div></div></div>
