<p id="mntl-sc-block_14-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Make hard sauce: stir together softened butter, confectioners&#39; sugar, vanilla extract, and milk. Sauce should be fairly stiff. Set aside.
</p>
