<div id="ugc-review__body-container_3-0" class="comp ugc-review__body-container mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__body_3-0" class="comp ugc-review__body mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__container_1-0" class="comp ugc-review__container mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__text_1-0" class="comp ugc-review__text mntl-text-block">This recipe is super easy and yummy. My kids (3 and 5) made these for breakfast and we used our mini waffle maker. We added chocolate sauce and marshmallows. Thanks so much!</div></div></div></div></div> </div>
