<div id="ugc-review__body-container_5-0" class="comp ugc-review__body-container mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__body_5-0" class="comp ugc-review__body mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__container_2-0" class="comp ugc-review__container mntl-block"><div id="ugc-review__text_2-0" class="comp ugc-review__text mntl-text-block">These turned out great. A lot of people saying they're not chocolate enough or sweet enough, waffles are meant to be topped with sweet items so they themselves aren't supposed to be super sweet. These were fluffy and did taste great as the recipe was. Thank you!</div></div></div></div></div> </div>
